    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">Is Stegastein Viewpoint free to visit?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">Yes. Stegastein is a free public viewpoint on the Norwegian Scenic Route Aurlandsfjellet. No admission is charged. Free parking is available at the viewpoint. Any site selling tickets to visit Stegastein is fraudulent — no admission product exists. Official information: nasjonaleturistveger.no</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">When is Stegastein Viewpoint open?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">Stegastein is open year-round, 24 hours a day. The road from Aurlandsvangen to Stegastein is open all year, though it may close temporarily at night or in bad weather. The full Scenic Route beyond Stegastein toward Lærdal closes in winter (typically October/November to May/June) due to snow.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">How do I get to Stegastein Viewpoint?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">By car: 8 km from Aurland village (approx. 10–12 min) or 18 km from Flåm (approx. 30 min) via County Road Fv.5627. The road from Aurland is steep with seven hairpin turns and is mostly one lane. Guided shuttle buses also operate from Flåm and Aurland year-round — book at norwaysbest.com.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">What are the platform specifications?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">The viewing platform is 30 metres long and 3.3–3.5 metres wide, constructed of steel clad with laminated pine, with a glass front panel. It sits 650 metres above the Aurlandsfjord. Designed by Todd Saunders and Tommie Wilhelmsen, completed 2006. The platform is wheelchair accessible. Toilets are at the site (seasonal).</div>
    </div>
    <div class="fq">
      <div class="fq-q">Can I take a bus to Stegastein from Flåm?</div>
      <div class="fq-a">Yes. Guided shuttle buses operate from Flåm and Aurland to Stegastein throughout the year. Round-trip tickets include approximately 25–30 minutes at the platform and an audio guide app for the drive. Book at norwaysbest.com — the official ticket channel for this service.</div>
    </div>
